channel.title: Use this project and make a track that’s around 60 seconds long!
channel.description:
You are only allowed to use the four sounds in the project link. No adding or deleting sounds. Other than that feel free to go crazy!!! Btw i added some loops already to inspire you.
P.S. Yes, this is meant for demo users to take part as well.
Enter by replying on this thread with your project link. Winner is chosen on Friday, March 15 at 9 PM EST. Have fun!!! :D
Project link: https://app.auxy.co/projects/KVkj3NYUpm-RCOkDk7Ik-g==
